# ================================================================
# 🔐 AUTH
# ================================================================

### 1. Register — Organizer
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ali Organizer",
  "email": "ali@test.com",
  "password": "pass123",
  "role": "organizer"
}

###

### 2. Register — Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sara Customer",
  "email": "sara@test.com",
  "password": "pass123",
  "role": "customer"
}

###

### 3. Login — Organizer (copy token → @organizerToken)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ali@test.com",
  "password": "pass123"
}

###

### 4. Login — Customer (copy token → @customerToken)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sara@test.com",
  "password": "pass123"
}

###

### 5. Get Current User — Organizer
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

###

### 6. Get Current User — Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

###


# ================================================================
# 📅 EVENTS — Public (no auth needed)
# ================================================================

### 7. Browse All Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events

###

### 8. Browse Events — With Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?page=1&limit=5

###

### 9. Browse Events — Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?status=upcoming

###

### 10. Get Single Event
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}

###


# ================================================================
# 📅 EVENTS — Organizer (requires organizer JWT)
# ================================================================

### 11. Create Event (copy _id from response → @eventId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Jaipur Literature Festival",
  "description": "The greatest literary show on earth, held annually in Jaipur.",
  "date": "2026-01-24T09:00:00.000Z",
  "venue": "Diggi Palace, Jaipur",
  "totalTickets": 100,
  "ticketPrice": 299
}

###

### 12. Create Second Event (to test multiple events)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Jaipur Tech Summit",
  "description": "Annual technology conference for developers and startups.",
  "date": "2026-03-10T10:00:00.000Z",
  "venue": "Hotel Clarks Amer, Jaipur",
  "totalTickets": 50,
  "ticketPrice": 999
}

###

### 13. Get My Events (organizer sees only their own)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/organizer/my
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

###

### 14. Update Event (triggers background notification job)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "venue": "Clarks Amer Hotel, Jaipur",
  "ticketPrice": 349
}

###

### 15. Update Event — Change Ticket Count
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalTickets": 150
}

###

### 16. Delete Event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

###

